%spark2

import spark.implicits._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

val fourElementsSchema = new StructType()
  .add(StructField("movieId", LongType, true))
  .add(StructField("userId", LongType, true))
  .add(StructField("rating", LongType, true))
  .add(StructField("date", DateType, true))

val fourElementsDF = spark.read
  .option("header", "true")
  .schema(fourElementsSchema)
  .parquet("/tmp/netflix-data-parquet")
  
fourElementsDF.show()
    
fourElementsDF.cache()

fourElementsDF.describe().show()

%spark2.sql

SELECT rating, COUNT(rating)
FROM movies
GROUP BY rating

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.{min, max}

FROM movies
WHERE date > CAST('2002-01-01' AS date)
AND date NOT IN ( CAST('2005-01-19' AS date), CAST('2005-04-06' AS date))
GROUP BY date
ORDER BY date ASC
